Durban

<img data-attachment-id="6122" data-permalink="https://www.newframe.com/durban-the-city-that-forces-the-poor-to-defecate-in-the-streets/dbn-stats/" data-orig-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS.png" data-orig-size="481,202" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="DBN STATS" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS-300x126.png" data-large-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS.png" src="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS.png" alt="" class="wp-image-6122" srcset="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS.png 481w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS-300x126.png 300w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DBN-STATS-480x202.png 480w" sizes="(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px" />

This city spokesperson says there are sufficient ablution facilities to meet demand. 
“To combat the contravention of our Nuisances and Behaviour in Public By-law, which prohibits urinating in public, the city has rolled out public urinals in the city centre.”
The spokesperson did not confirm how many public urinals were being rolled out. Toilets, she says, are cleaned five times a day.


